1.3
log
@Totally revamp the virtual device code.

Unbreak:
• floppy access (BIOS)
• hard disc access (BIOS)
• CD-ROM El Torito access (BIOS)
• cd9660, fat, ffs (filesystems)

Not tested:
• tftp, nfs (PXE, NET, filesystems)
• lmbmfs (lmbm)
@
